{"tid":945700,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣 發完屋企人脾氣之後先尼偷偷地後悔","createTime":"2018-12-18T05:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T18:12:51.000Z","uid":196499,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"303a2590ee2fbfaadbe87f2f1bdeb0827834c071","tid":945700,"uid":196499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"今朝起身趕住出門口<br />\n屋企個耆英平時已經出左門口但今日就係到沖涼霸住左廁所<br />\n個吓我好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心諗你又唔趕時間仲乜要同我爭啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就態度好差咁鬧佢 <br />\n而家係公司諗返好後悔 <br />\n儘管我冇講粗口 <br />\n但諗返我當時嘅態度係令佢幾咁難受 <br />\n可能佢有唔舒服先需要朝早尼沖涼 <br />\n我完全冇顧佢感受 <br />\n點解我可以咁衰對一個有份湊大自己嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04c03391b3830b7df8cf2b7d2a3233832b54eee","tid":945700,"uid":115119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:43:00.000Z","msg":"會，但係把口又講唔出好聽既說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fd3038a22b965aa1cd7507467b90e2b2371828","tid":945700,"uid":211004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"明"},{"pid":"59376463613986f4d1182ea8c1c3b48d8af845cd","tid":945700,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T18:12:51.000Z","msg":"有時會忍唔到口<br />\n事後瞬間勁後悔<br />\n<br />\n唯有之後氹番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}